[h1]Global Weapon Unboxing Simulator[/h1]

This game is all about Terrorist vs Counter Terrorist where both sides fight for control over stack of wooden boxes and .... pretty much thats it. 

Feel the rush in your body of being the last man alive on your team then do pathetic twitchy moments and cycle your weapons so you know what you're doing

This franchise was pretty dead until they let you decorate your weapon like a gun shaped Barbie.
